{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"37325e6728","title":"看了西安师院造反派两张大字报和给中央文革的信后的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"482cbd2640","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"37325e6728"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ada2e4ddb3","type":"paragraph","text":"五、伟大的战无不胜的马克思列宁主义[毛泽东思想]万岁","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"a123a19b22","type":"paragraph","text":"对姚文元同志纺间阿尔巴尼亚的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"a2a2c887b2","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）这次出去要注意谦虚啊！这不是一个代表团的问题，而且关系到中国红卫兵问题。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"232581d7b3","type":"paragraph","text":"关于超食静坐的间题","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"9e76db5990","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月二十九日）","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"c9bf1d9059","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义制度下，无产阶级专政条件下，绝食解坐可以做为一种斗争手段。因为无产阶级内部有一小摄敌人，有官擦主义。他无非要让你答应几个条件。所以绝食静坐，允许。但不能提倡，一般不赞成。绝食可以开水放糖、放盐、打葡萄糖，可以轮班。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"d16b14c0c2","type":"paragraph","text":"看了西安师院造反派两张大字报","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"beeaa01fd5","type":"paragraph","text":"和给中央交革的信后的批示","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"1b64d80854","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"fe0f293b57","type":"paragraph","text":"现在有的人是“铺张革命”，“大少爷作风”，“掌权开始，是浪费开始。”如果是人民内部矛盾的，批评人家宽一些，批评自己严一些。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"aa8b6d957f","type":"paragraph","text":"关于新甸间题的指示","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"5a68f50a45","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月一日）细甸问题不怕断交，不怕决裂，甚至于这个时候断交更好，这样更有利于我们放开手干。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"e147e3b1b9","type":"paragraph","text":"关于建造主席塑象周题的指示","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"2b21633a2f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月五日）林彪、恩来及文革小组各同志此类事是劳民伤财，无利有害，如不制止，势必会刮起一阵浮夸风。碰头会讨论一下发一指示，加以制止。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"6620a2d18e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"833f868f33","type":"paragraph","text":"七月五日","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"},{"id":"686fd0346e","type":"paragraph","text":"·317","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728"}],"page":{"id":"9f6548f60c","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"37325e6728","start":330,"end":330}}}},"__N_SSG":true}